short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A privacy first auto notes taker for Google Meet/Hangouts meetings.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Meets/Hangouts has this really cool live captions feature. This extension saves those captions as meeting notes. No meeting text or voice data is sent to any servers from this extension. All the processing happens on the client( your) end.
